owever, understand that the calendar has a life of its own now.  Calling for the deletion of the calendar because you have an issue?  Reality check.  Not only does that have zero chance of happening, but it reduces to near zero the credibility of whatever point you were trying to bring up in the first place.<br><br>Bear in mind, regardless of the origins and roots of the calendar, the #1 puprose of it today is to serve the masses of posting entities in sharing the planes.  Quest items for BB guilds are secondary.<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/umarcys.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Marcys</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Toede</span><br>  Posts: 51<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(11/13/00 12:07:06 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/marky_harlock/images/smmarcys.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Sirth sneaks into Hate </span><hr size=1> Who were the last 2 guilds in hate?<br> <p><table width="289" border="0"><tr><td width="48%"><div align="center"><img src="http://www.geocities.com/marky_harlock/images/marcys-small.jpg" width="113" height="113"></div></td></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ustygar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Stygar</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Toede</span><br>  Posts: 55<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(11/13/00 12:08:10 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.eqraid.org/images/characters/qwai.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Sirth sneaks into Hate </span><hr 